node.text:
drive away drops in a couple hours, and really quick just lemme say. 

since the day i made this song i knew it was so special. the luv i’ve already received on this track from friends & fam is unreal. i’m more then ready to share this with y’all & i know the whole team can agree with me on that. So please give it a listen & lmk what you think. luv y’all
